Vendored subset (the files needed to benchmark the qp-trie backend):
  Tbl.h, Tbl.c   — generic table API + dispatch layer
  qp.h,  qp.c    — the qp-trie backend
  README.md      — upstream description

NOTE: Tbl.c must be linked with exactly one backend implementation (here, qp.o).
Other backends in the upstream repo (fn, fp, wp, rc, cb, ...) export the same
Tbl symbols; linking the wrong one silently benchmarks a different structure.
